I just made this with bulgur, chicken stock (instead of water) and the crushed coriander. G-R-E-A-T.

Rating: 3
I made this as a side for straccetti di manzo. I found it easier to lightly pound the coriander seeds with a mallet. Toasting almonds is absolutely necessary. I used near east wheat salad mix without the seasoning packet, but forgot not to use the entire package of bulgar; The recipe only calls for a scant cup. It turned out okay (added more water). This may be good with lemon zest or dried fruits added.